{"tid":569783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【割地兩檢】藍絲撐高鐵 傅振中：議員要好似狗咁聽話勿拉布","createTime":"2018-02-23T04:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T06:38:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"25bb422c183f0249612891ab21e1b737bb58447a","tid":569783,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519359891_8e70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519359891_8e70.png&h=3da5867d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519359127_cde4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519359127_cde4.png&h=c8b92376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519359121_2390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519359121_2390.png&h=9a88dfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519359125_8fc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519359125_8fc0.png&h=00df6b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《廣深港高鐵（一地兩檢）條例草案》法案委員會今早舉行會議，有親中團體由金鐘港鐵站遊行至立法會，要求盡快完成審議高鐵一地兩檢。其中保衛香港運動主席傅振中指高鐵本應幾年前就通車，又指因為今年是狗年，「希望啲立法會嘅議員，好似狗一樣咁聽聽話話，不過佢哋嘅主人係我哋特區政府或者係中央政府，佢哋要支持人大決定去通過一地兩檢安排」。<br />\n<br />\n傅表示，高鐵是方便的交通工具，不希望民主派「阻住香港人去旅遊」。被問到是否要求議員不要監察政府，他回應稱是要求議員「唔好逆民意而行」，重申近年做的民調都顯示有逾50%市民支持實施一地兩檢，「大家都係想快啲返到內地，同接駁得到內地嘅交通工具，泛民話佢哋代表民主，咁就應該尊重民意。」<br />\n<br />\n他與珍惜群組一行約40人遊行至立法會示威區，並向立法會代表遞交請願信。另一親中團體「政中香港人」亦到場請願，指高鐵一地兩檢能方便港人往返內地，希望立法會盡快完成「三步走」最後一步的本地立法程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180223/57865032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57865032&d=N%2B2JqFz4pVhGsMQ0kZHqCp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=34f76c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57865032&h=14297e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180223/57865032</a>"},{"pid":"ae972b6f9e2d288f6bb23a2540fd6adfebd03330","tid":569783,"uid":158613,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"傅振中：議會是多餘的，帝制最好"},{"pid":"afc7110c95d12fef8e7c32c30a1fe36115645309","tid":569783,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"民選議員做政權隻狗<br />\n二百年前法國人都屌緊你"},{"pid":"f9b26a20049e40b1a5ddc1fe0c6287eba05a5841","tid":569783,"uid":87780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲廢中都生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc3ddb0ae8c1b744317fb0069519bef3d071d64","tid":569783,"uid":40628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"睇下五毛點答先"},{"pid":"3c03f337ec137c4d0ab239c36c3d0defb03a7b39","tid":569783,"uid":72186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n其實佢哋本身就咁閪蠢<br />\n定係扮出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9585ccd3cae364119b670f5c4de2481368038a93","tid":569783,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c03f337ec137c4d0ab239c36c3d0defb03a7b39","tid":569783,"uid":72186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n其實佢哋本身就咁閪蠢<br />\n定係扮出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.